    "description": "<i>Chill out on Skeeter’s Grid…</i><br>You play Skeet, master defragmenter, in this casual isometric puzzler. Reconstruct sectors, each of increasing complexity and variation, and meet the AI duo, who may or may not be benevolent. Collect cores along the way to improve your functions as you progress through this world of grids.<br><br><strong>Wishlist now! Skeeter's Grid is coming spring / summer 2023.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773440/extras/74144b1914e20251335bee6605d2d19a.avif?t=1679654165\" width=600 height=143 /></span><br><br><strong>A few features of note:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Randomly shuffled sectors with statistics recorded for every variation.<br></li><li> Bonus points and achievements for using every piece on the sector, or just speed-run through if that's your preference. It's up to you.<br></li><li> Original ambient soundtrack evolves as Skeet ascends from sector to sector.<br></li><li> Collect cores you'll need to augment Skeet's abilities, and learn about other daemons along the way.<br></li><li> Pick sides in a conflict between two AIs. The story evolves along with your choices.<br></li><li> Seamless transitions between sectors with zero loading.<br></li><li> Dozens of sectors, some quite massive, with a wide variety of pieces and functionalities.</li></ul><br>Skeeter's Grid fully supports gamepad (including Steam Deck) and keyboard (WASD).",
